{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a69890c90d","title":"给黄炎培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c9a3f3eff1","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":17,"articleId":"a69890c90d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wenji6","name":"毛泽东文集第六卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji6.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2a711a463d","type":"title","text":"给黄炎培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"f1cf6ba64c","type":"paragraph","text":"黄任老：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"2316a4808c","type":"paragraph","text":"刚才送上广东纠正宽大无边情报一份，现又送上广西的一份，请参阅。这两处是最典型的例子，其他地方不如此两处之甚，但亦天体相去不远，引起群众不满，极为普遍。不杀能首和惯，则能期不净，且越判越多。不杀恶霸，则农会不能组成，农民不敢分田。不杀重要的特务，则破坏暗杀层出不穷。总之，对首、恶霸、特务（重要的）必须采取坚决镇压的政策，群众才能翻身，人民政权才能巩固。当然，对可杀可不系的那一部分人，应当判处徒刑，或交群众监视，用劳动去改造之，不要系。如同宽天应有边，镇压也应有边，无边是不对的，已经解决了问题，群众已经满意了的地区，即不应再杀人了。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"9e0c22489f","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"04bd2de874","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"340f12af73","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十七日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"8db1ffbf33","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]黄炎培，字任之，民主建国会主要负责人，当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a69890c90d"}],"page":{"id":"cc8feb1dc1","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a69890c90d","start":122,"end":122}},"wenji6":{"comments":[{"id":"c82b4c2c4c","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"a69890c90d","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":4,"text":"黄炎培，字任之，中国民主建国会主要负责人。当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"044e65461d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"0c771816ae","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"16ed9a17d6","type":"title","text":"给黄炎培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"6b1f6999bf","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"c82b4c2c4c","type":"appellation","text":"黄任老：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"d0d64ef236","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"a69890c90d"},{"id":"ffb2c61764","type":"paragraph","text":"刚才送上广东纠正宽大无边情报一份，现又送上广西的一份，请参阅。这两处是最典型的例子，其他地方不如此两处之甚，但亦大体相去不远，引起群众不满，极为普遍。不杀匪首和惯匪，则匪剿不净，且越剿越多。不杀恶霸，则农会不能组成，农民不敢分田。不杀重要的特务，则破坏、暗杀层出不穷。总之，对匪首、恶霸、特务（重要的）必须采取坚决镇压的政策，群众才能翻身，人民政权才能巩固。当然，对可杀可不杀的那一部分人，应当判处徒刑，或交群众监视，用劳动去改造之，不要杀。如同宽大应有边，镇压也应有边，无边是不对的，已经解决了问题，群众已经满意了的地区，即不应再杀人了。顺致敬意！","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"a69890c90d"}],"page":{"id":"6e8e53e3e8","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"a69890c90d","start":155,"end":155}}}},"__N_SSG":true}